## WEB DEVELOPMENT ##

Flask:
    A framework to simplify common web server tasks.
    
    Structure:
        application.py
        requirements.txt
        static/
        templates/
        
    MVC Structure:
            Model - data (database, csv, ...)
          |       |
        updates  manipulates
          |       |
        view     controller 
       sees \   / uses
            user

    Render_template: uses {{ <var name> }} to reference http variables 


## DEFINITIONS ##

MVC: Model View Controller Paradigm.

Design Pattern: Ways to write code as a pattern.